INSERT INTO `blog_posts` VALUES (1,'Modern Farmhouse Plan: Perfect Design for Wide Shallow Lots with Outstanding Curb Appeal','modern-farmhouse-wide-shallow-lot-design','<h2>Exceptional Design for Challenging Lot Configurations</h2><p>Plan 1041 represents innovative architectural thinking, specifically crafted to maximize both functionality and curb appeal on wide, shallow lots. This <a href=\\\"https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plan/1041\\\">luxury modern farmhouse design</a> proves that lot limitations can inspire creative solutions rather than compromise your dream home vision.</p><h2>Thoughtfully Designed Main Floor Living</h2><p>The main floor showcases an expertly planned layout that emphasizes both daily living convenience and entertaining capabilities. The heart of the home features an expansive great room that seamlessly flows into the dining area, creating an open concept environment perfect for modern family life.</p><p>The kitchen serves as the command center, strategically positioned adjacent to a butler\'s pantry that provides exceptional storage and prep space. This thoughtful placement ensures efficient meal preparation while maintaining the clean, uncluttered aesthetic that defines contemporary living.</p><p>A private master suite occupies the main floor, offering convenient single-level living for homeowners who prefer to avoid stairs for their primary sleeping quarters. The master bathroom provides a luxurious retreat, while the nearby laundry room adds practical convenience to daily routines.</p><h2>Versatile Upper Level Configuration</h2><p>The second floor maximizes the home\'s potential with four additional bedrooms, each thoughtfully positioned to provide privacy and comfort. Multiple full bathrooms ensure morning routines run smoothly for busy families, while the expansive great room creates additional gathering space that can serve as a family room, game room, or flexible entertainment area.</p><p>This upper level design demonstrates how vertical space can be utilized effectively without compromising the home\'s wide, shallow footprint requirements.</p><h2>Impressive Four-Car Garage and Storage Solutions</h2><p>The substantial four-car garage addresses the storage and parking needs of active families while contributing to the home\'s impressive street presence. This generous garage space accommodates multiple vehicles, recreational equipment, and provides additional storage for seasonal items.</p><h2>Outdoor Living Integration</h2><p>Multiple porch areas extend the living space outdoors, creating seamless indoor-outdoor flow that enhances both daily living and entertaining opportunities. The spacious patio provides additional outdoor entertaining space, perfect for family gatherings and seasonal celebrations.</p><h2>Architectural Excellence for Wide Lot Optimization</h2><p>This design exemplifies how skilled architectural planning can transform lot challenges into design advantages. The elongated footprint creates impressive curb appeal while maximizing interior space utilization. Every square foot serves a purpose, from the practical butler\'s pantry to the flexible upper level great room.</p><p>Plan 1041 delivers the luxury and functionality that discerning homeowners expect, proving that thoughtful design can create exceptional homes regardless of lot configuration constraints.</p>','Discover this stunning modern farmhouse plan designed specifically for wide shallow lots. Features open concept living, 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and exceptional curb appeal that maximizes street frontage while maintaining elegant proportions and functional flow throughout.','modern-farmhouse','Quinn',NULL,'draft',15,0,NULL,'Modern Farmhouse Plan for Wide Shallow Lots | OchoWorks','Stunning modern farmhouse designed for wide shallow lots. 5BR/4BA with open concept living, great curb appeal. Complete construction-ready plans available.','2025-08-01 20:56:49','2025-10-23 14:09:18'),(2,'Spacious Single Story Ranch Home Plan with Open Concept Living and 3-Car Garage','spacious-single-story-ranch-open-concept-3-car-garage','<p>This stunning single-story ranch home combines modern functionality with timeless design, offering 3,494 square feet of thoughtfully planned living space. The open concept layout creates a seamless flow between the spacious great room, gourmet kitchen, and dining area, making it perfect for both everyday family life and entertaining guests.</p><h2>Open Concept Living at Its Finest</h2><p>The heart of this home features a <strong>generous great room</strong> that serves as the central gathering space, connected to a well-appointed kitchen with ample counter space and storage. The adjacent dining area provides the perfect setting for family meals and special occasions, while the <em>open floor plan</em> ensures natural light flows throughout the main living areas.</p><h2>Thoughtful Bedroom Layout</h2><p>The primary suite offers a private retreat with an <strong>ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet</strong>, positioned away from the secondary bedrooms for maximum privacy. Three additional bedrooms provide flexibility for family members, guests, or hobby spaces, each thoughtfully designed with natural light and adequate storage.</p><h2>Practical Home Office Solution</h2><p>A dedicated office space near the entry provides the perfect work-from-home solution, offering privacy for video calls while remaining easily accessible for clients or deliveries. This versatile room can also serve as a <em>formal dining room</em> or additional living space based on your family\'s needs.</p><h2>Convenient Daily Living Features</h2><p>The efficient laundry room connects the main living areas to the garage, creating a natural mudroom space for daily transitions. A well-positioned pantry provides additional kitchen storage, while the <strong>3-car garage</strong> offers plenty of room for your cars plus extra storage space for seasonal items and outdoor equipment.</p><h2>Indoor-Outdoor Connection</h2><p>The covered patio extends the living space outdoors, accessible from the main living areas and perfect for year-round entertaining. Large windows throughout the home bring in natural light and create a bright, welcoming atmosphere in every room.</p><h3>Why This Home Works</h3><p>This ranch home excels at providing <em>single-level living convenience</em> without sacrificing space or functionality. The thoughtful layout separates public and private areas while maintaining an open, connected feel throughout the main living spaces. With its combination of <strong>modern amenities and practical design</strong>, this home is ideal for growing families, empty nesters, or anyone seeking comfortable, accessible living.</p><p><a href=\'https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plan/1030\' target=\'_blank\'>View complete home details and additional images</a> to explore this exceptional single-story design further.</p>','Discover this exceptional single-story ranch home featuring an open concept great room, gourmet kitchen, luxurious primary suite, home office, and convenient 3-car garage. Perfect blend of modern functionality and timeless ranch design for comfortable family living.','single-story','Randy',NULL,'published',48,0,NULL,'Single Story Ranch Home Plan - 4BR/3BA with Open Concept','Beautiful single-story ranch house plan with open concept living, 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, home office, and 3-car garage. Custom home by OchoWorks Designs.','2025-08-08 13:13:58','2026-05-03 15:29:03'),(3,'Contemporary Two-Story Home with Open Concept Design and 3-Car Garage','contemporary-two-story-home-open-concept-3-car-garage','<p>This exceptional contemporary home combines modern architectural design with functional family living across two thoughtfully planned levels. The sophisticated exterior showcases clean lines, stucco construction, and an impressive arched entry that creates striking curb appeal.</p><h2>Main Floor Living at Its Finest</h2><p>The main floor features an <strong>open concept design</strong> that seamlessly connects the great room, kitchen, and dining nook, creating an ideal space for both daily family life and entertaining. The gourmet kitchen includes a convenient center island that provides additional workspace and casual dining options.</p><p>The luxurious <strong>primary suite</strong> occupies a private wing of the main floor, complete with an elegant ensuite bathroom featuring dual vanities and a spacious walk-in closet. This thoughtful placement ensures privacy and tranquility away from the home\'s active areas.</p><h2>Functional Spaces for Modern Living</h2><p>A dedicated <strong>home office</strong> provides the perfect workspace for remote work or study, while the convenient powder room serves guests without compromising privacy. The utility room keeps laundry tasks organized and out of sight.</p><p>The covered patio extends living space outdoors, creating seamless indoor-outdoor entertaining opportunities. The <strong>3-car garage</strong> offers plenty of room for cars plus additional storage for tools, equipment, and seasonal items.</p><h2>Upper Level Family Zone</h2><p>The second floor creates a dedicated family zone with a generous <strong>family room</strong> that serves as a perfect retreat for relaxation or casual entertainment. Three additional bedrooms provide comfortable accommodations for family members or guests, while two full bathrooms ensure convenience for the upper level.</p><h2>Contemporary Design Excellence</h2><p>This home exemplifies contemporary architectural principles with its emphasis on <strong>clean lines</strong>, geometric forms, and functional beauty. The stucco exterior requires minimal maintenance while providing lasting durability and modern aesthetic appeal.</p><h3>Perfect for Growing Families</h3><p>The two-story layout maximizes square footage while maintaining efficient use of lot space. The separation of the primary suite on the main floor from secondary bedrooms upstairs provides privacy for parents while keeping family areas connected and accessible.</p><h2>Builder-Friendly Design</h2><p>Developed by OchoWorks Designs with over 30 years of construction experience, this contemporary home features practical construction details that ensure efficient building and long-term functionality. Every element has been carefully considered for both aesthetic appeal and construction practicality.</p><p><strong>Ready to build your dream contemporary home?</strong> <a href=\\\"https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plan/1024\\\">Contact us today</a> to learn more about this exceptional design and explore customization options that perfectly match your vision and lifestyle needs.</p>','Discover this stunning contemporary two-story home featuring an open concept great room, gourmet kitchen with island, luxurious primary suite, dedicated office, and spacious 3-car garage. Perfect blend of modern style and functional family living.','contemporary','Randy',NULL,'published',87,0,NULL,'Contemporary Two-Story Home Plans | OchoWorks Designs','Modern two-story home with open concept living, primary suite, office, 3-car garage. Custom contemporary house plans by OchoWorks Designs.','2025-08-15 13:52:12','2026-05-03 13:49:21'),(6,'Stunning 6-Bedroom Modern Farmhouse with Open Concept Living and 4-Car Garage','6-bedroom-modern-farmhouse-open-concept-4-car-garage','<p>This magnificent two-story modern farmhouse combines contemporary functionality with timeless farmhouse appeal, creating the perfect home for large families who value both style and practicality.</p><h2>Open Concept Main Floor Living</h2><p>The heart of this home features a <strong>seamlessly connected great room, kitchen, and dining area</strong> that creates an ideal space for daily family life and entertaining. The gourmet kitchen serves as the centerpiece, perfectly positioned to overlook the great room while maintaining easy access to the dining area and outdoor patio.</p><p>A dedicated office provides the perfect work-from-home solution, offering privacy and productivity without sacrificing connection to the main living areas. The convenient butler\'s pantry ensures ample storage and preparation space for the busy family kitchen.</p><h2>Luxurious Master Suite Retreat</h2><p>The main floor master suite offers a private sanctuary with an <em>generously sized bedroom</em> and spa-like master bathroom. The thoughtful layout includes a spacious walk-in closet and direct access to the laundry room, making daily routines effortless.</p><h2>Upstairs Recreation and Bedroom Wing</h2><p>The upper level transforms into a family haven with four additional bedrooms and a <strong>spacious recreation room</strong> perfect for movie nights, game time, or relaxation. Each bedroom is thoughtfully designed with adequate storage and natural light, while multiple full bathrooms ensure morning routines run smoothly.</p><h3>Practical Storage Solutions</h3><p>Smart storage solutions throughout the home include a dedicated storage room upstairs and multiple closets, ensuring everything has its place in this well-organized family home.</p><h2>Impressive 4-Car Garage</h2><p>The oversized garage provides <strong>plenty of room for four cars</strong> while offering additional space for storage, workshop activities, or seasonal items. This substantial garage adds significant value and functionality to the home.</p><h2>Perfect for Growing Families</h2><p>With over 6,000 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space, this modern farmhouse accommodates large families, multi-generational living, or those who love to host guests. The combination of private retreats and gathering spaces creates the ideal balance for modern family life.</p><p>Ready to explore this exceptional design? <a href=\'https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plan/1028\' target=\'_blank\'>View complete specifications and additional details</a> for this stunning modern farmhouse.</p>','Discover this exceptional two-story modern farmhouse featuring 6 bedrooms, 7.5 bathrooms, open concept great room, gourmet kitchen, luxurious master suite, upstairs recreation room, and spacious 4-car garage. Perfect for large families seeking contemporary comfort with farmhouse charm.','modern-farmhouse','Quinn',NULL,'draft',28,0,NULL,'6-Bedroom Modern Farmhouse Design | OchoWorks Plans','Exceptional 2-story modern farmhouse with 6 bedrooms, 7.5 baths & 4-car garage. Over 6,100 sq ft of open-concept luxury living. Custom home plans by OchoWorks.','2025-08-22 20:21:12','2026-03-03 21:39:40'),(7,'Modern Single-Story Ranch Home with Open Concept and 3-Car Garage','modern-single-story-ranch-home-open-concept-3-car-garage','<p>This stunning single-story ranch home combines modern functionality with timeless appeal, offering everything today\'s families need in a thoughtfully designed layout. With an open concept living area, spacious kitchen, and well-appointed bedrooms, this home delivers comfort and convenience in every square foot.</p><h2>Open Concept Living at Its Finest</h2><p>The heart of this home features a <strong>seamless open concept design</strong> that connects the great room, dining area, and kitchen into one expansive living space. This flowing layout is perfect for both everyday family life and entertaining guests, creating an inviting atmosphere where conversations can flow naturally from room to room.</p><h2>Gourmet Kitchen with Modern Amenities</h2><p>The well-designed kitchen serves as the centerpiece of the home, featuring ample counter space and a convenient <strong>walk-in pantry</strong> for all your storage needs. The kitchen\'s strategic placement allows the cook to remain connected with family and guests in the adjoining great room and dining areas.</p><h2>Thoughtful Bedroom Layout</h2><p>This home offers a <strong>split bedroom design</strong> that provides privacy and tranquility. The luxurious master bedroom is positioned away from the other bedrooms, creating a peaceful retreat complete with a <em>spacious walk-in closet</em> and a well-appointed master bathroom.</p><p>Three additional bedrooms provide flexibility for growing families, home offices, or guest accommodations. Each bedroom is designed with comfort in mind, offering natural light and efficient use of space.</p><h2>Practical Living Features</h2><p>The home includes several features that enhance daily living:</p><ul><li><strong>Dedicated laundry room</strong> for convenience and organization</li><li><strong>Three full bathrooms</strong> strategically placed throughout the home</li><li><strong>Covered front porch</strong> that adds curb appeal and provides a welcoming entrance</li><li><strong>Spacious patio</strong> perfect for outdoor dining and relaxation</li></ul><h2>Generous 3-Car Garage</h2><p>The oversized garage provides <strong>plenty of room for three cars</strong> plus additional storage space for tools, seasonal items, and recreational equipment. This generous storage solution keeps your vehicles protected while maintaining an organized home environment.</p><h2>Why Choose This Ranch Design</h2><p>Single-story living offers numerous advantages, from <em>accessibility and convenience</em> to easier maintenance and energy efficiency. This ranch home eliminates the need for stairs, making it ideal for families of all ages and those planning to age in place.</p><p>The efficient 1,997 square foot layout maximizes every inch while maintaining comfortable room proportions throughout. The thoughtful design ensures no wasted space while providing all the amenities modern families desire.</p><p><a href=\'https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plan/1039\'>View complete details and specifications for this exceptional ranch home</a> to see how it can transform your vision of the perfect family home into reality.</p>','Discover this exceptional single-story ranch home featuring an open concept great room, gourmet kitchen, luxurious primary suite, and convenient 3-car garage. Perfect for modern family living with thoughtful design and functionality.','ranch','Randy',NULL,'draft',21,0,NULL,'Modern Ranch Home - Open Concept 4BR/3BA with 3-Car Garage','Single-story ranch home with open concept living, 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and 3-car garage. Perfect family design with thoughtful layout and functionality','2025-08-29 21:04:22','2026-03-03 21:42:57'),(9,'Stunning Two-Story Modern Traditional Home with Open Concept Living and Master Suite','two-story-modern-traditional-open-concept-master-suite','<p>This stunning two-story modern traditional home combines timeless architectural elements with contemporary living spaces to create the perfect family retreat. Designed for both comfort and entertaining, this exceptional home offers an ideal blend of formal and casual living areas.</p><h2>Open Concept Main Floor Living</h2><p>The heart of this home features a beautifully designed open concept layout that seamlessly connects the <strong>spacious great room</strong>, gourmet kitchen, and dining area. This flowing floor plan creates an inviting atmosphere perfect for daily family life and entertaining guests. The kitchen serves as the central hub, offering easy access to both the dining area and great room while maintaining excellent sight lines throughout the main living spaces.</p><h2>Luxurious Master Suite Retreat</h2><p>The main floor master bedroom provides a private sanctuary away from the busy family areas. This <strong>generous master suite</strong> includes a <em>convenient home office</em>, making it perfect for today\'s work-from-home lifestyle. The thoughtful placement on the main floor offers privacy and convenience, while the adjoining office space provides a quiet workspace without sacrificing bedroom comfort.</p><h2>Flexible Guest Accommodations</h2><p>A well-appointed guest room on the main floor offers comfortable accommodations for visitors, complete with easy access to a nearby bathroom. This thoughtful design element ensures guests feel welcome while maintaining the family\'s privacy in the upstairs bedrooms.</p><h2>Upper Level Family Spaces</h2><p>The second floor features four additional bedrooms, providing ample space for growing families. The highlight of the upper level is the <strong>expansive bonus room</strong>, offering endless possibilities as a family room, playroom, media center, or recreational space. A charming loft area adds extra flexibility, perfect for a reading nook, study area, or additional storage.</p><h2>Practical Design Elements</h2><p>The home includes essential practical features that make daily life more convenient:</p><ul><li>Three-car garage providing plenty of room for cars and storage</li><li>Dedicated laundry room for efficient household management</li><li>Walk-in pantry for kitchen organization and storage</li><li>Multiple bathrooms strategically placed throughout both floors</li><li>Covered porch creating an welcoming entry experience</li><li>Patio area extending outdoor living opportunities</li></ul><h2>Modern Traditional Style Architecture</h2><p>The exterior showcases beautiful modern traditional design elements, featuring clean lines balanced with classic architectural details. <em>Exposed beam accents</em> and multiple gabled rooflines create visual interest while maintaining the home\'s sophisticated appeal. The thoughtful combination of materials and proportions results in a timeless design that will remain stylish for years to come.</p><p>This exceptional home design successfully balances the needs of modern family living with classic architectural appeal, making it an ideal choice for families seeking both style and functionality in their dream home.</p><p>Ready to make this stunning home yours? <a href=\'https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plan/1027\'>View complete details and specifications</a> to learn more about this exceptional design and begin your journey toward building your dream home.</p>','Discover this exceptional two-story modern traditional home featuring an open concept great room, gourmet kitchen, main floor master suite with office, spacious bonus room, and convenient 3-car garage. Perfect for growing families seeking style and functionality.','modern-traditional','Randy',NULL,'published',41,0,NULL,'Two-Story Modern Traditional Home - Open Concept Design','Stunning two-story modern traditional home with open concept living, main floor master suite, bonus room, and 3-car garage. Perfect for growing families.','2025-09-01 21:40:35','2026-05-03 07:25:08'),(10,'Modern Farmhouse with 6 Bedrooms, Open Concept Living & Rec Room','modern-farmhouse-6-bedroom-open-concept-rec-room-1-1','<p>This exceptional two-story modern farmhouse combines contemporary living with timeless farmhouse charm, creating the perfect home for growing families. The thoughtfully designed layout maximizes both functionality and comfort across two levels.</p><h2>Open Concept Main Floor Living</h2><p>The heart of this home centers around the <strong>open concept great room and kitchen</strong>, creating an ideal space for daily family life and entertaining. The spacious great room flows seamlessly into the gourmet kitchen, while the adjacent dining room provides a dedicated space for family meals and special occasions.</p><p>The main floor also features a convenient <strong>home office</strong>, perfect for remote work or managing household tasks. Practical amenities include a well-positioned laundry room and pantry for efficient daily routines.</p><h2>Luxurious Primary Suite</h2><p>The main floor primary suite offers a private retreat with an <em>expansive master bedroom</em> and luxurious ensuite bathroom. This convenient single-level primary suite placement provides easy accessibility while maintaining separation from the home\'s active areas.</p><h2>Additional Bedrooms and Recreation Space</h2><p>The upper level expands the home\'s living potential with <strong>three additional bedrooms</strong> and two full bathrooms, providing ample space for family members and guests. The standout feature is the <em>generous recreation room</em>, offering endless possibilities for family entertainment, game nights, or relaxation.</p><h2>Practical Family Features</h2><p>This modern farmhouse includes several family-friendly features:</p><ul><li>Six total bedrooms for growing families</li><li>Five and a half bathrooms for convenience</li><li>Dedicated office space for work-from-home needs</li><li>Three-car garage with plenty of room for cars and storage</li><li>Welcoming front porch for outdoor relaxation</li><li>Efficient laundry room placement</li></ul><h2>Modern Farmhouse Style</h2><p>The exterior showcases classic <strong>modern farmhouse architecture</strong> with clean lines, dormer windows, and a welcoming front porch supported by columns. This timeless design ensures lasting curb appeal while providing all the modern amenities today\'s families desire.</p><p>Whether you\'re looking for a home that accommodates multi-generational living, provides dedicated spaces for work and play, or simply offers room for your family to grow, this modern farmhouse delivers on all fronts with its perfect blend of style and functionality.</p><p>Ready to explore this design further? <a href=\'https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plan/1042\'>View complete plan details and specifications</a> to see how this modern farmhouse could become your dream home.</p>','Discover this stunning two-story modern farmhouse featuring 6 bedrooms, 5.5 bathrooms, an open concept great room and kitchen, dedicated office space, spacious recreation room, and 4-car garage. Perfect for growing families seeking style and functionality.','modern-farmhouse','Quinn',NULL,'published',88,0,NULL,'5 Bedroom Modern Farmhouse with Open Concept & Rec Room','Two-story modern farmhouse with 5 bedrooms, 4 baths, open concept living, home office, recreation room & 2-car garage. Perfect for growing families.','2025-09-18 21:50:13','2026-05-03 10:52:48'),(11,'Spacious Single-Story Ranch Home with Open Concept Living and 3-Car Garage','spacious-single-story-ranch-home-open-concept-living-3-car-garage-1','<p>This beautifully designed single-story ranch home offers the perfect blend of comfort, functionality, and style for modern family living. With generous living spaces and thoughtful details throughout, this home provides everything you need for comfortable everyday life and effortless entertaining.</p><h2>Open Concept Living at Its Finest</h2><p>The heart of this home centers around a <strong>spacious great room</strong> that flows seamlessly into the dining area and kitchen, creating an inviting space perfect for family gatherings and entertaining guests. The open layout ensures everyone stays connected whether you\'re preparing meals, relaxing, or hosting friends.</p><h2>Gourmet Kitchen Design</h2><p>The <strong>well-appointed kitchen</strong> features a large center island that provides abundant workspace and casual seating. A convenient walk-in pantry keeps your kitchen organized and clutter-free, while the thoughtful layout makes meal preparation a pleasure.</p><h2>Luxurious Primary Suite</h2><p>Retreat to your private <strong>primary bedroom suite</strong> complete with a spa-like bathroom and generous walk-in closet. This peaceful sanctuary offers the perfect escape at the end of each day.</p><h2>Three Additional Bedrooms</h2><p>Three comfortable <strong>secondary bedrooms</strong> provide plenty of space for family members or guests. Two bedrooms share a well-designed hall bathroom with dual vanities, while a third bedroom enjoys private access to another full bathroom.</p><h2>Entertainment and Recreation</h2><p>A dedicated <strong>game room</strong> offers the ideal space for family fun, whether you\'re setting up a pool table, creating a home theater, or designing the ultimate entertainment zone for kids and adults alike.</p><h2>Functional Spaces</h2><p>Practical features enhance daily living, including a <strong>dedicated office</strong> perfect for working from home, a convenient mudroom off the garage entry, and a well-placed laundry room. The covered deck extends your living space outdoors, ideal for morning coffee or evening relaxation.</p><h2>3-Car Garage</h2><p>The <strong>oversized garage</strong> provides plenty of room for three cars plus additional storage space for tools, sports equipment, and seasonal items.</p><h2>Single-Story Convenience</h2><p>Everything you need is on one level, making this home perfect for families of all ages. The efficient layout eliminates stairs while maximizing comfort and accessibility.</p><p>This exceptional ranch home combines timeless style with modern functionality, creating a welcoming space your family will love for years to come.</p>','Discover this exceptional single-story ranch home featuring an open concept great room, gourmet kitchen with expansive island, luxurious primary suite, three additional bedrooms, and a convenient 3-car garage. Perfect for families seeking comfortable one-level living with modern amenities and thoughtful design.','ranch','Quinn',NULL,'published',80,0,NULL,'4-Bedroom Ranch Home | Open Concept | 3-Car Garage','Spacious single-story ranch home with open layout, 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, gourmet kitchen, primary suite & 3-car garage. Perfect for families.','2025-09-30 21:39:24','2026-05-03 08:35:18'),(12,'Stunning Two-Story Contemporary Home with RV Garage and Rooftop Deck - 4 Bedrooms, 5 Baths','stunning-two-story-contemporary-home-rv-garage-rooftop-deck-1','<p>This exceptional two-story contemporary home redefines modern living with its impressive blend of style, functionality, and thoughtful design. Spanning over 4,000 square feet, this architectural masterpiece offers everything today\'s families need for comfortable, sophisticated living.</p><h2>Open Concept Main Floor Living</h2><p>The main floor welcomes you with a generous open concept layout that seamlessly connects the great room, dining area, and gourmet kitchen. This flowing design creates the perfect environment for both everyday family life and entertaining guests. The kitchen features a well-appointed layout with a convenient pantry for ample storage, while the adjacent dining space offers easy access to the outdoor patio.</p><h2>Luxurious Primary Suite</h2><p>The main floor primary suite serves as a private retreat, complete with a spacious ensuite bathroom designed for relaxation and comfort. The thoughtful placement on the main level provides convenient single-story living when desired, while maintaining separation from the entertaining spaces.</p><h2>Impressive Garage Options</h2><p>One of the standout features of this home is the exceptional garage space. The 2-car garage provides plenty of room for your cars and storage needs, while the additional RV garage offers a rare and valuable amenity for homeowners with recreational vehicles, boats, or equipment. This versatile space can also serve as a workshop or hobby area.</p><h2>Expansive Upper Level</h2><p>The upper floor delivers exceptional versatility with two additional bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and a generous entertainment room perfect for a home theater, game room, or family gathering space. A flexible office area provides the ideal spot for remote work or study. The crowning feature is the rooftop deck, offering an exceptional outdoor living space with sweeping views.</p><h2>Contemporary Design Excellence</h2><p>The home\'s contemporary architecture features clean lines, mixed materials, and striking modern aesthetics that create impressive curb appeal. Large windows throughout flood the interior with natural light while maintaining the home\'s sleek, sophisticated appearance.</p><h2>Perfect for Growing Families</h2><p>With four bedrooms and five bathrooms spread across two well-planned levels, this home accommodates growing families, multi-generational living, or frequent guests with ease. The combination of open living spaces and private retreats ensures everyone has room to thrive.</p><p>Whether you\'re an owner-builder looking for a comprehensive design or working with a contractor, this contemporary home delivers construction-ready plans that bring exceptional living to life. The thoughtful layout maximizes every square foot while creating distinct zones for living, entertaining, and relaxation.</p>','Discover this remarkable two-story contemporary home featuring 4 bedrooms, 5 bathrooms, and over 4,000 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space. The main floor showcases an open concept great room, gourmet kitchen, luxurious primary suite, and an impressive 2-car garage plus RV garage. Upstairs, enjoy a spacious entertainment room, three additional bedrooms, and access to a stunning rooftop deck perfect for outdoor living.','contemporary','Randy',NULL,'published',76,0,NULL,'Contemporary Home with RV Garage | OchoWorks Designs','4-bedroom, 5-bath contemporary home with RV garage, rooftop deck, and 4,000+ sq ft. Open concept living, luxurious primary suite, and 2-car plus RV garage.','2025-10-31 20:34:38','2026-05-03 13:35:47'),(13,'Single-Story Modern Farmhouse with Open Concept Living – 3 Bed, 2 Bath, 1,595 Sq Ft','single-story-modern-farmhouse-open-concept-living-3bed-2bath-1','<h2>A Modern Farmhouse Designed for How You Actually Live</h2><p>If you\'ve been searching for a single-story home that blends timeless curb appeal with a smart, functional layout, this <strong>Modern Farmhouse</strong> is worth a very close look. At <strong>1,595 square feet</strong>, it delivers everything a growing family or downsizing couple needs — without the wasted space.</p><p>Board-and-batten siding, natural stone accents, a charming dormer, and a welcoming covered front porch give this home unmistakable character from the street. Step inside and the open, flowing layout immediately sets the tone.</p><h2>Open Concept Living at Its Best</h2><p>The heart of the home is a generous <strong>great room</strong> that connects seamlessly to the dining area and kitchen, creating one continuous living space ideal for everyday family life and entertaining alike. Natural light pours in through well-placed windows, keeping the space bright and inviting throughout the day.</p><p>The <strong>kitchen</strong> is thoughtfully positioned at the center of it all — close enough to the dining and great room to keep the cook part of the conversation, yet defined enough to feel purposeful. Whether you\'re prepping a weeknight dinner or hosting friends on the weekend, the layout just works.</p><h2>A Private Master Suite Built to Recharge</h2><p>Tucked away from the secondary bedrooms for maximum privacy, the <strong>master suite</strong> is a true retreat. It features a <strong>walk-in closet</strong> and a dedicated <strong>master bath</strong> — everything you need to start and end the day on your own terms.</p><h2>Two Comfortable Additional Bedrooms</h2><p>Two well-proportioned secondary bedrooms share a full <strong>hallway bath</strong>, making this layout ideal for families with children, guests, or a home office setup. Each bedroom includes closet storage, keeping the living areas clutter-free.</p><h2>Smart Everyday Functionality</h2><p>A dedicated <strong>laundry room</strong> keeps household chores out of sight and out of the way. The <strong>2-car garage</strong> gives you plenty of room for your cars, bikes, and weekend gear. Out back, a <strong>rear patio</strong> extends your living space outdoors, while the <strong>covered front porch</strong> adds that classic farmhouse welcome.</p><h2>Ready to Build on Your Lot</h2><p>With a compact <strong>58\'9\" x 49\'4\" footprint</strong>, this home fits comfortably on a wide range of lot sizes while still delivering a layout that feels open and spacious. At OchoWorks Designs, every plan we deliver is <strong>construction-ready</strong> — drawn with 30+ years of building experience behind every line.</p><p>Whether you\'re an <strong>owner-builder</strong> managing your own project or working with a <strong>contractor</strong>, our complete plan sets include site plans, foundation plans, floor framing, electrical layouts, elevations, roof plans, and wall sections — everything your builder needs to break ground with confidence.</p><p><a href=\'https://ochoworksdesigns.com\'>Explore all of our Modern Farmhouse designs at OchoWorks Designs</a> and find the home that fits your vision, your lot, and your life.</p><h3>Quick Specs</h3><ul><li><strong>Style:</strong> Modern Farmhouse</li><li><strong>Stories:</strong> Single Story</li><li><strong>Bedrooms:</strong> 3</li><li><strong>Bathrooms:</strong> 2</li><li><strong>Total Living Area:</strong> 1,595 sq ft</li><li><strong>Footprint:</strong> 58\'9\" x 49\'4\"</li><li><strong>Garage:</strong> 2-Car</li><li><strong>Outdoor Living:</strong> Covered Front Porch, Rear Patio</li></ul>','Discover this stunning single-story Modern Farmhouse featuring an open concept great room, well-appointed kitchen, private master suite with walk-in closet, two additional bedrooms, covered front porch, rear patio, and a 2-car garage — all in an efficient 1,595 sq ft footprint built for comfortable everyday living.','modern-farmhouse','Randy',NULL,'published',0,0,NULL,'Modern Farmhouse Ranch Home | 3 Bed 2 Bath 1595 Sq Ft','Single-story Modern Farmhouse with open concept great room, master suite, 3 beds, 2 baths, and 2-car garage. Construction-ready plans from OchoWorks Designs.','2026-03-03 21:57:44','2026-03-03 21:57:44');
