INSERT INTO `email_campaigns` VALUES (1,1,'Intro','Home plans for upcoming builds',NULL,'{{salutation}}  \n\nI wanted to reach out and introduce myself. My name is Randy Stewart with OchoWorks Designs and Drafting, a family-run company with over 30 years of home-building experience. We create clear, construction-ready home plans that are practical to build from and help prevent delays or confusion during construction.  \n\nWe work closely with builders on their subdivisions to create home designs that fit the character, lot sizes, and goals of the neighborhood. We’re also glad to work with your homeowners if they don’t have plans yet, helping them develop something that fits their needs and budget. For spec homes, we can create plans that are simple, repeatable, or tailored to a specific lot.  \n\nHere’s a quick overview of what we offer for builders: https://ochoworksdesigns.com/home-builders  \n\nIf you have an upcoming project you’d like us to look at, we’d be glad to help.  \n\nThanks, \nRandy \nOchoWorks Designs and Drafting \n(435) 680-1907 \nrandy@ochoworksdesigns.com',1,'OchoWorks Designs and Drafting','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com',0,'sent',NULL,'2026-04-30 21:26:10',NULL,194,245,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-04-30 21:26:10','2026-04-30 21:26:10'),(3,2,'First Test Email','First Test Email',NULL,'{{salutation}}\n\nThis is a test.\n{{link_url_1}}\n\nThanks',1,'OchoWorks Designs and Drafting','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com',0,'sent',NULL,'2026-02-24 18:45:22',NULL,0,2,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-02-24 18:45:22','2026-02-24 18:45:22'),(4,1,'Contact Info','Residential House Plans',NULL,'{{salutation}}\n\nMy name is Randy Stewart, and I wanted to take a moment to introduce myself. I run OchoWorks Designs and Drafting, a family‑run company with over 30 years of home‑building experience. We provide clear, construction‑ready home plans that are practical to build from and help reduce delays or confusion during construction.\n\nIf you have clients who don’t have plans yet, I’m happy to work with you and your homeowners to create something that fits their needs and their budget. I also assist with plan modifications and fully custom designs when needed.\n\nHere’s a quick overview of what I offer for builders:\n{{link_url_1}}\n\nIf you have an upcoming project you’d like me to review, I’d be glad to help.\n\nThanks,\nRandy\nOchoWorks Designs and Drafting\n(435) 680‑1907\nrandy@ochoworksdesigns.com',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'sent',NULL,'2026-02-24 20:18:49',NULL,0,1,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-02-24 20:18:49','2026-02-24 20:18:49'),(5,1,'Contact Info','Residential House Plans',NULL,'{{salutation}}\n\nMy name is Randy Stewart, and I wanted to take a moment to introduce myself. I run OchoWorks Designs and Drafting, a family‑run company with over 30 years of home‑building experience. We provide clear, construction‑ready home plans that are practical to build from and help reduce delays or confusion during construction.\n\nIf you have clients who don’t have plans yet, I’m happy to work with you and your homeowners to create something that fits their needs and their budget. I also assist with plan modifications and fully custom designs when needed.\n\nHere’s a quick overview of what I offer for builders:\n{{link_url_1}}\n\nIf you have an upcoming project you’d like me to review, I’d be glad to help.\n\nThanks,\nRandy\nOchoWorks Designs and Drafting\n(435) 680‑1907\nrandy@ochoworksdesigns.com',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'draft',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-02-24 20:16:30','2026-02-24 20:16:30'),(6,1,'Just Spoke on phone','Residential House Plans',NULL,'{{salutation}}\n\nThis is Randy Stewart with OchoWorks Designs and Drafting we just spoke on the phone.\n\nWe are family-run company with over 30 years of home-building experience. We create clear, construction-ready home plans that are practical to build from and help prevent delays or confusion during construction.\n\nWe work closely with builders on their subdivisions to create home designs that fit the character, lot sizes, and goals of the neighborhood. We’re also glad to work with your homeowners if they don’t have plans yet, helping them develop something that fits their needs and budget. For spec homes, we can create plans that are simple, repeatable, or tailored to a specific lot.\n\nHere is a link to our website:\n{{link_url_1}}\n\nIf you have an upcoming project you’d like us to look at, we’d be glad to help.\n\nThanks,\nRandy\n(435) 680-1097\nochoworksdesigns.com',1,'OchoWorks Designs and Drafting','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com',0,'sent',NULL,'2026-03-05 20:42:54',NULL,0,3,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-03-05 20:42:54','2026-03-05 20:42:54'),(7,1,'Follow up on intro email, where no response','Build Ready plans for your upcoming projects',NULL,'{{salutation}}  \n\nI\'m following up on an email I sent and wanted to make sure you have my contact information so we can be considered for your next home.\n\nMy name is Randy Stewart with OchoWorks Designs and Drafting. We\'re a family‑run business with over 30 years of home‑building experience, and we create clear, construction‑ready home plans that help prevent delays and confusion during construction.\n\nWe work closely with builders on subdivisions to create home designs that fit the character, lot sizes, and goals of the neighborhood. We\'re also glad to work directly with your homeowners if they need plans, and we can produce simple, repeatable spec plans or tailor designs to specific lots.\n\nIf you\'d like to see examples, here are some of our featured plans: https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plans\n\nIf you have specific requirements — for example, size, footprint, number of bedrooms, or budget — I can email you a few plan ideas tailored to those needs. \n\nThanks, \nRandy \nOchoWorks Designs and Drafting \n(435) 680-1907 \nrandy@ochoworksdesigns.com',1,'OchoWorks Designs and Drafting','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com',0,'sent',NULL,'2026-04-16 19:33:50',NULL,0,25,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-04-16 19:33:50','2026-04-16 19:33:50'),(9,1,'Follow up on text conversations','Build Ready plans for your upcoming projects',NULL,'{{salutation}}  \n\nI\'m following up on our recent text conversation and wanted to make sure you have my contact information so we can be considered for your next home.  \n\nMy name is Randy Stewart with OchoWorks Designs and Drafting. We\'re a family-run firm with over 30 years of home-building experience, and we create clear, construction-ready home plans that help prevent delays and confusion during construction.  \n\nWe work closely with builders on subdivisions to create home designs that fit the character, lot sizes, and goals of the neighborhood. We\'re also glad to work directly with your homeowners if they need plans, and we can produce simple, repeatable spec plans or tailor designs to specific lots.  \n\nIf you\'d like to see examples, here are some of our featured plans: https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plans  \n\nIf you have some specific requirements — for example size, footprint, number of bedrooms, or budget — I can email you a few plan ideas tailored to those needs.  \n\nThanks, \nRandy \nOchoWorks Designs and Drafting \n(435) 680-1907 \nrandy@ochoworksdesigns.com',1,'OchoWorks Designs and Drafting','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com',0,'sent',NULL,'2026-04-02 21:35:50',NULL,0,7,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-04-02 21:35:50','2026-04-02 21:35:50'),(11,1,'Follow up on a recent phone call','Build Ready plans for your upcoming projects','Follow up on a recent phone call to keep me in mind','{{salutation}}\n\nI’m following up on our recent phone call and wanted to make sure you have my contact information so we can be considered for your next home.\n\nMy name is Randy Stewart with OchoWorks Designs and Drafting. We\'re a family-run company with over 30 years of home‑building experience, creating clear, construction‑ready home plans.\n\nOur work with builders includes subdivision design, ensuring each home fits the character, lot sizes, and goals of the neighborhood. I can provide simple, repeatable spec plans or tailor designs to specific lots, and I’m also glad to work directly with your homeowners if they need plans.\n\nIf you\'d like to see examples, here are some of our featured plans: https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plans\n\nIf you have specific requirements — size, footprint, number of bedrooms, or budget — I can email you a few plan ideas tailored to those needs.\n\nThanks,\nRandy\nOchoWorks Designs and Drafting\n(435) 680-1907\nrandy@ochoworksdesigns.com',1,'OchoWorks Designs and Drafting','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com',0,'sent',NULL,'2026-04-28 19:32:39',NULL,0,10,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-04-28 19:32:39','2026-04-28 19:32:39'),(12,1,'Follow up on not recent phone call','Build Ready plans for your upcoming projects',NULL,'{{salutation}}\n\nI’m following up on our phone call we had a while back and wanted to make sure you have my contact information so we can be considered for your next home.\n\nMy name is Randy Stewart with OchoWorks Designs and Drafting. We\'re a family-run company with over 30 years of home‑building experience, creating clear, construction‑ready home plans.\n\nOur work with builders includes subdivision design, ensuring each home fits the character, lot sizes, and goals of the neighborhood. I can provide simple, repeatable spec plans or tailor designs to specific lots, and I’m also glad to work directly with your homeowners if they need plans.\n\nIf you\'d like to see examples, here are some of our featured plans: https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plans\n\nIf you have specific requirements — size, footprint, number of bedrooms, or budget — I can email you a few plan ideas tailored to those needs.\n\nThanks,\nRandy\nOchoWorks Designs and Drafting\n(435) 680-1907\nrandy@ochoworksdesigns.com',1,'OchoWorks Designs and Drafting','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com',0,'sent',NULL,'2026-04-28 21:08:36',NULL,0,53,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-04-28 21:08:36','2026-04-28 21:08:36'),(13,1,'Follow up on recent email','Build Ready plans for your upcoming projects',NULL,'{{salutation}}\n\nI’m following up on our recent email and wanted to make sure you have my contact information so we can be considered for your next home.\n\nMy name is Randy Stewart with OchoWorks Designs and Drafting. We\'re a family-run company with over 30 years of home‑building experience, creating clear, construction‑ready home plans.\n\nOur work with builders includes subdivision design, ensuring each home fits the character, lot sizes, and goals of the neighborhood. I can provide simple, repeatable spec plans or tailor designs to specific lots, and I’m also glad to work directly with your homeowners if they need plans.\n\nIf you\'d like to see examples, here are some of our featured plans: https://ochoworksdesigns.com/plans\n\nIf you have specific requirements — size, footprint, number of bedrooms, or budget — I can email you a few plan ideas tailored to those needs.\n\nThanks,\nRandy\nOchoWorks Designs and Drafting\n(435) 680-1907\nrandy@ochoworksdesigns.com',1,'OchoWorks Designs and Drafting','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com',0,'sent',NULL,'2026-04-07 21:09:37',NULL,0,1,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-04-07 21:09:38','2026-04-07 21:09:38'),(14,1,'Intro with pricing','Home Plans for Upcoming Builds',NULL,'{{salutation}}\n\nI wanted to reach out and introduce myself. My name is Randy Stewart with OchoWorks Designs and Drafting, a family-run company with over 30 years of home-building experience. We create clear, construction-ready home plans that are practical to build from and help prevent delays or confusion during construction.\n\nWe work closely with builders on their subdivisions to create home designs that fit the character, lot sizes, and goals of the neighborhood. We’re also glad to work with your homeowners if they don’t have plans yet, helping them develop something that fits their needs and budget. For spec homes, we can create plans that are simple, repeatable, or tailored to a specific lot.\n\nHere’s a quick overview of what we offer for builders: https://ochoworksdesigns.com/home-builders\n\nFor reference, our pricing is straightforward:\n - Purchase existing plans without major changes is $1.00/sf.\n - Fully custom home designs are $1.25–$2.00/sf depending on style of home.\n\nThe square footage price is for the living area only. We do not charge for garages, patios, or porches.\n\nIf you have an upcoming project you’d like us to look at, we’d be glad to help.\n\nThanks,\nRandy\nOchoWorks Designs and Drafting\n(435) 680-1907\nrandy@ochoworksdesigns.com',1,'OchoWorks Designs and Drafting','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com','randy@ochoworksdesigns.com',0,'sent',NULL,'2026-04-07 21:35:55',NULL,0,1,0,0,0,0,NULL,'2026-04-07 21:35:56','2026-04-07 21:35:56');
